{"tid":997842,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(大陸戲注意)有無人有睇《影》劇透討論","createTime":"2019-01-27T13:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T15:12:11.000Z","uid":134812,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"099ff794beaca895c5c80a883155833ed663c66b","tid":997842,"uid":134812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://assets.wmoov.com/movie/photo/201812/FB_IMG_1544860691986_1545094216.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.wmoov.com%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201812%2FFB_IMG_1544860691986_1545094216.jpg&h=bfc35d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n古時紛爭的年代，對於要奪回被敵國霸佔的境州城，沛國都督子虞（鄧超 飾）和沛王沛良（鄭愷 飾）有著截然不同的主張。子虞違背沛王的求和之計，隱藏於暗處，指揮從小被秘密囚禁的影子替身境州（鄧超 飾），決定抗命進攻境州城。 這場殘酷的權謀之爭隨之展開。一個個爾虞我詐互相操控，君臣、夫妻、影子與真身的關係交織著。一系列陰謀亦開始浮出水面，為國為家的人不過是為了個人利益。 被推著上戰場的影子若想為了自己而活，不再成為他人的棋子，就必須蛻變和重新掌控自己的命運&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u-hy-KyLuCY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du-hy-KyLuCY&d=VkPAZ4LKujINdWeCQe5UZY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=81071aac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u-hy-KyLuCY</a><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"1cccec56a81865b53f0f49578967c7f9ac322f44","tid":997842,"uid":134812,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"好似無乜人講呢套<br />\n難得佢係開放式結局諗住同大家開個po講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姑勿論佢係大陸戲<br />\n套嘢啲畫面真係好鬼靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面打戲嗰啲慢動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n仲要睇完播cast先知男主係一人分飾兩角<br />\n好戲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n整體嚟講真係幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家唔會因為係大陸戲而Miss咗佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">除咗攻城嗰下笑到我抽筋</span>"},{"pid":"63c2184aef4a7bc1baf8677e74de128ee5074aa9","tid":997842,"uid":134812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"有無巴打入嚟講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f6a45457f92381852e066135ce1e79e2a7e3dc","tid":997842,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d5e3ad7a18e9f9d31e2f132adc9a8e18a055fcb","tid":997842,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"套劇好似係講三國"},{"pid":"cd7cdb3111aee38a9f2f3cccacb4a1a5b5f841e2","tid":997842,"uid":134812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d5e3ad7a18e9f9d31e2f132adc9a8e18a055fcb","tid":997842,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"套劇好似係講三國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"失荊州改編<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5696968e45a3a06923e3b9c3d059f4343642041c","tid":997842,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"大陸成半年前上映<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86ffcab67abddcb7f41db856a50f5501f849983","tid":997842,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:28:27.000Z","msg":"故弄玄虛 執黑澤明啲口水尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbed8c0575d23dea3c86538d0d0097d0fdac43a","tid":997842,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"上網一睇<br />\n已經無哂場數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f55357b879936985c85ccfda622c19550265bc","tid":997842,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"鄧超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 孫儷<img src=\"/as